title: Email Server Down - Unable to Send/Receive Emails
description: Critical email server outage affecting all departments. Users cannot send or receive emails. Server shows connectivity issues and needs immediate attention.

title: Printer Not Working in Office Floor 3
description: HP LaserJet printer in the 3rd floor office is not responding to print jobs. Paper jam indicator is off, but device shows offline status.

title: Application Crash on Login
description: Customer management application crashes immediately after user authentication. Error occurs consistently across multiple user accounts.
resolutionNotes: Root cause identified as corrupted user session cache. Cleared cache and updated authentication module. Issue resolved.

title: Network Connectivity Issues in Building A
description: Intermittent network connectivity in Building A affecting approximately 50 workstations. Users experience slow internet and frequent disconnections.

title: Database Performance Degradation
description: Customer database queries running significantly slower than normal. Response times increased from 2s to 15s average.
resolutionNotes: Database indexes were fragmented. Performed index rebuild and optimization. Query performance restored to normal levels.

title: Software License Expiration Warning
description: Microsoft Office licenses for 25 workstations are expiring in 30 days. Need to renew licenses to avoid service interruption.

title: VPN Connection Timeout Issues
description: Remote employees experiencing frequent VPN connection timeouts. Connections drop every 15-20 minutes requiring reconnection.
resolutionNotes: VPN server configuration updated with increased timeout values and connection pool optimization. Issue resolved.

title: Mobile App Crashing on Android Devices
description: Company mobile application crashes on Android devices running OS version 12 and above. iOS devices are unaffected.
